  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nA user with an AMD Opteron 6172 CPU reported regular SIGILLs when using a binary they'd compiled themselves. Such CPUs are pretty rare in the wild, and I think they need the portable flag turned on in BLST, even when compiling from source.\r\n\r\n## Version\r\n\r\nLighthouse v1.0.2\r\n",
